com.microsoft.bingads.v11.bulk

Class BulkUploadOperation

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.microsoft.bingads.v11.bulk.BulkOperation<UploadStatus>
      • com.microsoft.bingads.v11.bulk.BulkUploadOperation

  • public class BulkUploadOperation
extends BulkOperation<UploadStatus>
    Represents a bulk upload operation requested by a user.

    Example: BulkServiceManager.submitUploadAsync(com.microsoft.bingads.v11.bulk.FileUploadParameters, com.microsoft.bingads.AsyncCallback<com.microsoft.bingads.v11.bulk.BulkUploadOperation>) method returns an instance of this class. If for any reason you do not want to wait for the file to finish uploading, for example if your application quits unexpectedly or you have other tasks to process, you can use an instance of BulkUploadOperation to download the upload results file when it is available.
